data.description: Lots of character with this 3/2/2 block home on 1.2 acres in Valrico with NO HOA or CDD. Large front yard, back yard and side yard!! The home is completely fenced in with a new wooden fence. Brick on the outside gives it a true ranch design. Plenty of room to park your boat or RV! The interior features a large split floor plan with vaulted ceilings and two skylights in the family room adding natural light and a wood burning fireplace with brick surrounding it adding character. The kitchen has been recently updated with all stainless-steel appliances, granite countertops, and a spacious breakfast bar and walk in pantry. The large master bedroom has its own sliding glass door entrance to the completely enclosed back screened in patio and a newly renovated shower plus a large walk-in closet with extra built-in shelving. New brick pavers extend past the huge screened in patio (14x40) for more outside enjoyment. There are 2 other spacious bedrooms both with walk in closets and laminate flooring. New Lamanite flooring in the main living areas and freshly painted inside. Roof 2016. Quiet and private and just moments away from all the shopping and restaurants in Valrico and very close to the Crosstown and I75 getting you to Tampa in just a short amount of time. Hard to find land in Valrico, this one won't last long!
